snippet.title: CTHULOOT - Demo Trailer Coop Fest
snippet.description:
CTHULOOT is a cooperative multiplayer (online & couch) party game where players loot mysterious locations on behalf of Cthulhu.

You can wishlist the game on Steam or try a demo of the game with your friends: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2283410/CTHULOOT/

Join the discord: https://discord.gg/FwUwUchAhw
